        <item>
            <title>1.2.0</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2026 03:24:14 +0800</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/wangwanjie/MachOKnife/releases/tag/v1.2.0</link>
            <sparkle:version>3</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.2.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown">## Highlights

- rebuilt the main browser around a MachOKit-backed tree with grouped summaries, lazy loading, copy/export actions, and richer `Detail` / `Data` views
- added archive-aware parsing, summary, contamination check, merge, and split workflows in both the GUI and `machoe-cli`
- expanded tool windows for Retag and XCFramework packaging, including drag and drop, cancellation, adaptive styling, and native-toolchain packaging helpers
- improved preferences, localization refresh, update strategy handling, and recent-file reopening for security-scoped bookmarks
- adopted a CocoaPods workspace for Debug-only `ViewScopeServer` integration and updated release scripts to package from the workspace
</description>
